OL,5,Crunning away
OL,7,FA teenage boy with severe learning
OL,8,Fdifficulties and a "strong attraction"
OL,9,Fto water drowned in a river after
OL,10,Fgoing missing from his grandparents'
OL,11,Fhouse, an inquest heard.
OL,13,FLuke Howe, who had ADHD and autism
OL,14,Fspectrum disorder, was found dead in
OL,15,Fthe River Bollin, near Ashley Road in
OL,16,FHale, Trafford, on 19 January 2024.
OL,18,FHis family said Luke was impulsive
OL,19,Fwith a lack of fear, and often got
OL,20,Finto dangerous situations without
OL,21,Frealising it.
