OL,7,FThe inquest heard the 14-year-old,
OL,8,Ffrom Sale, disappeared from his
OL,9,Fgrandparents' home, sparking a major
OL,10,Fsearch in freezing temperatures
OL,11,Finvolving police, friends, family,
OL,12,Fneighbours and his teachers.
OL,14,FWitnesses who drove past Luke reported
OL,15,Fseeing him running along nearby roads
OL,16,Fin the area with his school uniform
OL,17,Fon. His body was found in the River
OL,18,FBollin by a police diver the next day.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
