OL,4,Cattraction' to water drowned after
OL,5,Crunning away
OL,7,FLuke's father, James Howe, told the
OL,8,Finquest that his son escaped regularly
OL,9,Ffrom his home and from his specialist
OL,10,Fschool, Brentwood Community College,
OL,11,Fparticularly when he was in an excited
OL,12,Fstate.
OL,14,F"Running off and escaping continued to
OL,15,Fbe a strong impulse for him," said Mr
OL,16,FHowe.
OL,18,FHe said his son's conditions made him
OL,19,Fimpulsive with a lack of fear and said
OL,20,Fhe often got into dangerous situations
OL,21,Fwithout even realising it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
