OL,4,Cattraction' to water drowned after
OL,5,Crunning away
OL,7,FMr Howe said Luke had a "strong
OL,8,Fattraction" to water and detailed a
OL,9,Fnumber of previous occasions when he
OL,10,Fhad ran off and jumped into canals or
OL,11,Frivers, saying he was also excited
OL,12,Fwhen the emergency services attended.
OL,14,FHe was also hospitalised several times
OL,15,Fafter swallowing coins, the inquest
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
