OL,4,Cattraction' to water drowned after
OL,5,Crunning away
OL,7,F"He loved spending time with his
OL,8,Ffamily," Mr Howe told the inquest. "He
OL,9,Fmanaged to make me smile even when we
OL,10,Fwere in hospital. Luke was a real
OL,11,Fcharacter who was well known in the
OL,12,Farea. He hated staying in the house.
OL,14,F"He liked going camping and on
OL,15,Fholidays together. Luke loved spending
OL,16,Ftime with both sets of his
OL,17,Fgrandparents. He was a very cuddly
OL,18,Fboy. He was really a very loving
OL,19,Fperson.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
