OL,3,CBoy with autism and 'strong
OL,4,Cattraction' to water drowned after
OL,5,Crunning away
OL,7,F"His death has been a huge loss to his
OL,8,Ffamily and everyone who knew him. He
OL,9,Fis very sadly missed and is in our
OL,10,Fhearts everyday."
OL,12,FMr Howe said Luke was "really happy"
OL,13,Fand was "really well supported" at
OL,14,Fschool.
OL,16,FThe inquest heard Luke was reviewed by
OL,17,Fthe Child and Adolescent Mental Health
OL,18,FService every three months and had a
OL,19,Fcarer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
