OL,7,FHe was also prescribed a range of
OL,8,Fmedication. The inquest heard the
OL,9,Ffamily believed his care package was
OL,10,Fdue to be increased at the end of the
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FMr Howe detailed the huge lengths the
OL,14,Ffamily went to to keep Luke safe. They
OL,15,Ffitted chiming sensors to all the
OL,16,Fdoors and used internal locks, key
OL,17,Fsafes and window locks.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
