OL,7,FDetective Inspector Richard Lees, from
OL,8,FTrafford CID, said he couldn't rule
OL,9,Fout whether Luke had slipped or jumped
OL,10,Fin from a bridge. The tragic death, he
OL,11,Fadded, wasn't treated as suspicious.
OL,13,FThere were steep embankments on either
OL,14,Fside of the stretch of the river where
OL,15,FLuke was found and the temperature was
OL,16,F'extremely cold' with ice on the
OL,17,Fground, he added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
