OL,7,FAfter giving his evidence, Detective
OL,8,FInspector Lees said police officers
OL,9,Ftry to put emotion aside, but Luke's
OL,10,Fdeath had touched a lot of people.
OL,12,FA pathologist who carried out a post-
OL,13,Fmortem examination gave a cause of
OL,14,Fdeath as drowning.
OL,16,FThe inquest at Stockport Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt is listed for three days.
